<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Relat√≥rio Nutricional - [[${paciente.nomeCompleto}]]</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #2c3e50;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* HEADER */
        .header {
            overflow: hidden;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #4361ee;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #4361ee;
            font-size: 22pt;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .header-info {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }

        /* PATIENT BANNER */
        .patient-banner {
            background-color: #4361ee;
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 25px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .patient-banner .name {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .patient-banner .details {
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .patient-banner .contact {
            font-size: 9pt;
            margin-top: 6px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* SECTIONS */
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 14pt;
            color: #1e293b;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        /* STATS TABLE */
        .stats-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .stats-table td {
            width: 33.33%;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 8pt;
            color: #64748b;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 24pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4361ee;
            display: block;
        }

        .stat-unit {
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        /* COMPOSITION */
        .composition-box {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-left: 5px solid #3b82f6;
            padding: 18px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .comp-grid {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .comp-grid td {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
        }

        .comp-label {
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #475569;
        }

        .comp-value {
            font-size: 14pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3b82f6;
            float: right;
        }

        /* OBJECTIVE */
        .objective-badge {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 5px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #78350f;
        }

        .objective-badge strong {
            color: #92400e;
        }

        /* DATA TABLE */
        .data-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .data-table th {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            color: #334155;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 9pt;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .data-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        .data-table tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }

        .data-table .value-col {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #475569;
        }

        /* INFO BOX */
        .info-box {
            background-color: #dcfce7;
            border-left: 5px solid #10b981;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #065f46;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .info-box p {
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #064e3b;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* HEALTH INFO */
        .health-grid {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .health-grid td {
            padding: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .health-grid td:first-child {
            width: 40%;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }

        .health-grid td:last-child {
            width: 60%;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        /* FOOTER */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 8pt;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .footer .warning {
            color: #dc2626;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* PAGE BREAK */
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 1.5cm;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- HEADER -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>RELAT√ìRIO NUTRICIONAL</h1>
            <div class="header-info">
                <strong>Data da Consulta:</strong> <span th:text="${dataConsultaFormatada}">00/00/0000</span> | 
                <strong>Gerado em:</strong> <span th:text="${#dates.format(#dates.createNow(), 'dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm')}"></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- PATIENT BANNER -->
        <div class="patient-banner">
            <div class="name" th:text="${paciente.nomeCompleto}">Nome do Paciente</div>
            <div class="details">
                <strong>Idade:</strong> <span th:text="${idadePaciente}">0</span> anos | 
                <strong>Sexo:</strong> <span th:text="${paciente.sexo}">-</span> | 
                <strong>CPF:</strong> <span th:text="${paciente.cpf}">000.000.000-00</span>
            </div>
            <div class="contact" th:if="${paciente.telefoneWhatsapp != null or paciente.email != null}">
                <span th:if="${paciente.telefoneWhatsapp != null}">üì± <span th:text="${paciente.telefoneWhatsapp}">-</span></span>
                <span th:if="${paciente.email != null and paciente.email != ''}"> | üìß <span th:text="${paciente.email}">-</span></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- OBJECTIVE -->
        <div class="objective-badge" th:if="${questionario != null and questionario.objetivo != null}">
            <strong>Objetivo:</strong> <span th:text="${questionario.objetivo}">-</span>
        </div>

        <!-- COMPOSI√á√ÉO CORPORAL -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">üìä Composi√ß√£o Corporal</div>

            <table class="stats-table">
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <span class="stat-label">Peso</span>
                        <span class="stat-value">
                            <span th:text="${avaliacaoFisica != null and avaliacaoFisica.pesoAtual != null ? #numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.pesoAtual, 1, 1) : '-'}">0.0</span>
                        </span>
                        <span class="stat-unit" th:if="${avaliacaoFisica != null and avaliacaoFisica.pesoAtual != null}">kg</span>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <span class="stat-label">Altura</span>
                        <span class="stat-value">
                            <span th:text="${avaliacaoFisica != null and avaliacaoFisica.altura != null ? #numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.altura, 1, 2) : '-'}">0.00</span>
                        </span>
                        <span class="stat-unit" th:if="${avaliacaoFisica != null and avaliacaoFisica.altura != null}">m</span>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <span class="stat-label">IMC</span>
                        <span class="stat-value">
                            <span th:text="${avaliacaoFisica != null and avaliacaoFisica.imc != null ? #numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.imc, 1, 1) : '-'}">0.0</span>
                        </span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <div class="composition-box" th:if="${avaliacaoFisica != null}">
                <table class="comp-grid">
                    <tr th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.massaMagra != null}">
                        <td>
                            <span class="comp-label">üí™ Massa Magra</span>
                            <span class="comp-value"><span th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.massaMagra, 1, 2)}">0.00</span> kg</span>
                        </td>
                        <td th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.massaGorda != null}">
                            <span class="comp-label">üìâ Massa Gorda</span>
                            <span class="comp-value"><span th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.massaGorda, 1, 2)}">0.00</span> kg</span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.percentualGordura != null}">
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <span class="comp-label">üìä Percentual de Gordura</span>
                            <span class="comp-value"><span th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.percentualGordura, 1, 1)}">0.0</span>%</span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- PER√çMETROS -->
        <div class="section" th:if="${avaliacaoFisica != null}">
            <div class="section-title">üìè Per√≠metros Corporais</div>
            
            <table class="data-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Regi√£o</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Medida (cm)</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.perimetroOmbro != null and avaliacaoFisica.perimetroOmbro > 0}">
                        <td>Ombro</td>
                        <td class="value-col" th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.perimetroOmbro, 1, 1)}">0.0</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.perimetroTorax != null and avaliacaoFisica.perimetroTorax > 0}">
                        <td>T√≥rax</td>
                        <td class="value-col" th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.perimetroTorax, 1, 1)}">0.0</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.perimetroCintura != null and avaliacaoFisica.perimetroCintura > 0}">
                        <td>Cintura</td>
                        <td class="value-col" th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.perimetroCintura, 1, 1)}">0.0</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.perimetroAbdominal != null and avaliacaoFisica.perimetroAbdominal > 0}">
                        <td>Abdominal</td>
                        <td class="value-col" th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.perimetroAbdominal, 1, 1)}">0.0</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.perimetroQuadril != null and avaliacaoFisica.perimetroQuadril > 0}">
                        <td>Quadril</td>
                        <td class="value-col" th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.perimetroQuadril, 1, 1)}">0.0</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.perimetroBracoDireitoContr != null and avaliacaoFisica.perimetroBracoDireitoContr > 0}">
                        <td>Bra√ßo Direito (Contra√≠do)</td>
                        <td class="value-col" th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.perimetroBracoDireitoContr, 1, 1)}">0.0</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.perimetroCoxaDireita != null and avaliacaoFisica.perimetroCoxaDireita > 0}">
                        <td>Coxa Direita</td>
                        <td class="value-col" th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.perimetroCoxaDireita, 1, 1)}">0.0</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr th:if="${avaliacaoFisica.perimetroPanturrilhaDireita != null and avaliacaoFisica.perimetroPanturrilhaDireita > 0}">
                        <td>Panturrilha Direita</td>
                        <td class="value-col" th:text="${#numbers.formatDecimal(avaliacaoFisica.perimetroPanturrilhaDireita, 1, 1)}">0.0</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <!-- ESTILO DE VIDA -->
        <div class="section" th:if="${questionario != null}">
            <div class="section-title">üèÉ Estilo de Vida</div>
            
            <table class="health-grid">
                <tr th:if="${questionario.frequenciaTreino != null}">
                    <td>Frequ√™ncia de Treino:</td>
                    <td th:text="${questionario.frequenciaTreino}">-</td>
                </tr>
                <tr th:if="${questionario.tempoTreino != null}">
                    <td>Tempo de Treino:</td>
                    <td th:text="${questionario.tempoTreino}">-</td>
                </tr>
                <tr th:if="${questionario.qualidadeSono != null}">
                    <td>Qualidade do Sono:</td>
                    <td th:text="${questionario.qualidadeSono}">-</td>
                </tr>
                <tr th:if="${questionario.ingestaoAguaDiaria != null}">
                    <td>Ingest√£o de √Ågua:</td>
                    <td><span th:text="${questionario.ingestaoAguaDiaria}">0</span> litros/dia</td>
                </tr>
                <tr th:if="${questionario.funcionamentoIntestino != null}">
                    <td>Funcionamento Intestinal:</td>
                    <td th:text="${questionario.funcionamentoIntestino}">-</td>
                </tr>
                <tr th:if="${questionario.pressaoArterial != null}">
                    <td>Press√£o Arterial:</td>
                    <td th:text="${questionario.pressaoArterial}">-</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <!-- HIST√ìRICO DE SA√öDE -->
        <div class="section" th:if="${questionario != null and (questionario.medicamentos != null or questionario.suplementos != null)}">
            <div class="section-title">üíä Hist√≥rico de Sa√∫de</div>
            
            <div class="info-box" th:if="${questionario.medicamentos != null and questionario.medicamentos != ''}">
                <h3>Medicamentos em Uso</h3>
                <p th:text="${questionario.medicamentos}">-</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-box" th:if="${questionario.suplementos != null and questionario.suplementos != ''}">
                <h3>Suplementos</h3>
                <p th:text="${questionario.suplementos}">-</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FOOTER -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><span class="warning">‚ö†Ô∏è Importante:</span> Este relat√≥rio cont√©m orienta√ß√µes gerais baseadas em avalia√ß√£o nutricional.</p>
            <p>Para acompanhamento personalizado, mantenha consultas regulares com seu nutricionista.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <strong>Nutritional Plan Assistant</strong> | 
                Paciente: <span th:text="${paciente.nomeCompleto}">-</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>